data.message: Add token-resolution visibility to devkit report: Added ResolutionStats tracking + _format_resolution_stats() function. Devkit output now includes resolution.health grade (excellent/good/degraded/blind), resolved_pct, and breakdown by source (arbitrary/css_var/best_effort/unresolved). CI logs will now reveal if verifier is blind.
